    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324540/extras/e42d7ccf759609dd3923dcd381e74af5.poster.avif?t=1767969271\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324540/extras/e42d7ccf759609dd3923dcd381e74af5.webm?t=1767969271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324540/extras/e42d7ccf759609dd3923dcd381e74af5.mp4?t=1767969271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伴随着活力四射的音乐，在颜色鲜明的关卡中穿梭，让飞船的颜色与流场颜色保持同步，在避开危险障碍的同时引导你前进。 保持警惕，不要走错路！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >伴随音乐流动</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>匹配颜色：</strong>跟随流场颜色的变化切换飞船的颜色，快速通过每个关卡。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动感音乐：</strong>强劲有力、令人血脉喷张的背景音乐推动着游戏的进行。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特关卡：</strong>手工制作的形态可以不断升级，具有独特的视觉风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无限重玩： </strong>进入愤怒模式，将挑战推向新的高度！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发现捷径</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到隐藏路径，更快地通过关卡！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324540/extras/9833ecfb20182e7136b2ae3b86287728.poster.avif?t=1767969271\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324540/extras/9833ecfb20182e7136b2ae3b86287728.webm?t=1767969271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324540/extras/9833ecfb20182e7136b2ae3b86287728.mp4?t=1767969271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >通过狂暴模式提高热度</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁狂暴模式，提高你的速度。 没有限制，看看你到底能跑多快？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324540/extras/5fb37403b626a736a0d788aa12df182d.poster.avif?t=1767969271\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324540/extras/5fb37403b626a736a0d788aa12df182d.webm?t=1767969271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324540/extras/5fb37403b626a736a0d788aa12df182d.mp4?t=1767969271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
